## 🌟 Project Highlights

💼 Project	Description
🎨 Turtle Race	An interactive GUI game using OOP and randomization
🔔 Rain Alert	Uses OpenWeather API + Twilio to send SMS alerts
🏋 Workout Tracker	Integrates Google Sheets API to log workouts
🎵 Spotify Time Machine	Web scraper + API to recreate past playlists
📈 Habit Tracker	Visual graph API with user authentication
🚀 Capstone	A full-stack app with authentication and deployment

## 🛠 Tech & Tools
	•	Python 3.10+
	•	turtle, tkinter, pandas, requests, json
	•	Web scraping: BeautifulSoup, Selenium
	•	Web APIs: Twilio, Pixela, Spotify, Sheety, OpenWeather
	•	Flask, HTML/CSS, Bootstrap, RESTful API Design
	•	Git/GitHub, Markdown documentation

